CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 19, 1945 page 13 reads: "Poster Contest Winners - Winners in high school competition sponsored by the Pittsburgh Branch of Federal Union, Inc., pose with their entries at Carnegie Museum. Left to right: Joseph Schumacher, junior at Connelley Vocational School; John Wall, senior at Peabody High; Roland Lucas, senior at South Hills High" - Harris Photo
TitMainTitle: Joseph Schumacher holding sign inscribed "Unite through Federal Union," next to case with feathered masks
